{"tid":476780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"🐘🐘🐘其實燒毀象牙，係咪真有用","createTime":"2017-11-22T10:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T10:11:23.000Z","uid":49648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0a28ccb213ff36d4cd4120f7af3881017dcb7ef","tid":476780,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"長久以來，銷毀象牙被視為對抗野生動物產品非法交易的一種英勇表現，但很多人卻沒意識到這些行動的負面後果。銷毀象牙會造成可用來起訴全球盜獵者的寶貴法醫資料因此消失，也通常會使世界各地的象牙需求量增加──導致更多的盜獵情形。如果行動主義者真的想阻止盜獵，應該致力於提高反盜獵行動的效果、加強象牙需求國家的執法力度和減少消費者的需求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f3b2b67ffbb22ea41f8d9c4382c263949726da","tid":476780,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:11:23.000Z","msg":"買象牙返來燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}